## Per-Carat Value Analysis: Where the Math Actually Lands

Here's the real ranking by cost efficiency — so you can see exactly what you're paying per carat:

| Bracelet | Total Price | Carat Weight | $/ct | Diamond Type |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| 2-Prong Lab 5ct White Gold (sale) | $3,374 | 5ct | **$675** | Lab |
| 4-Prong Lab 3ct White Gold (sale) | $2,485 | 3ct | **$828** | Lab |
| Princess Lab 5ct White Gold (sale) | $4,396 | 5ct | **$879** | Lab |
| JA Flower Clasp Lab 2ct White Gold | $2,015 | 2ct | **$1,008** | Lab |
| Emerald Cut Lab 5ct White Gold | $5,710 | 5ct | **$1,142** | Lab |
| Oval Lab 5ct White Gold | $5,780 | 5ct | **$1,156** | Lab |
| JA Flower Clasp Natural 2ct Yellow | $3,445 | 2ct | **$1,723** | Natural |
| Bezel Natural 2ct Yellow Gold (sale) | $3,561 | 2ct | **$1,781** | Natural |
| Emerald Cut Natural 5ct (sale) | $8,029 | 5ct | **$1,606** | Natural |
| Natural Round 3ct White Gold | $5,870 | 3ct | **$1,957** | Natural |
| Floating Natural 3ct White Gold | $6,020 | 3ct | **$2,007** | Natural |
