**Key insight:** The two-prong lab 5ct at $675/ct is exceptional value if you want maximum diamond presence. But notice that the natural 3ct bestseller at $5,870 only costs $1,957/ct — that's not dramatically more per carat than some of the natural options at lower total prices. The volume discount on natural bracelets is real.

